{
  "text": " You didn't start your business to do admin, but every week hours disappear into invoicing, scheduling, client follow-ups and paperwork. Sound familiar. Rizflow maps your workflows, finds exactly where time and money leak and builds custom AI agents that handle all of it automatically. Your agents plug into Slack, HubSpot, Telegram, Notion and 50 more tools you already use. No rip and replace. Go live in two to four weeks, then it just runs. Admin, CAHM's, Billing, Scheduling, 24.7. You cut operating costs by up to 60%. You reclaim 20 plus hours every week, and you check everything from your phone in under 30 minutes. But we don't just handle admin. Rizflow agents track inventory, manage supply chains, and automate stock taking for trading businesses, retail, F and B and logistics. Real-time stock alerts, purchase order automation, supplier coordination. Every unit accounted for every reorder timed perfectly. Don't just take our word for it. Rain fresh and e-commerce brand came to us buried in manual orders and stock mismatches. Within weeks, our agents cut their order processing time by 70% in eliminated stockouts entirely. Real client, real results, scale your business, not your workload. Get your free discovery audit at Rizflow.co.",
